Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.94,0:26:25.15,opp,,0,0,0,,世界誕生的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.17,0:26:28.94,opp,,0,0,0,,在生命之樹之下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.97,0:26:31.87,opp,,0,0,0,,兩人聆聽著遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.21,0:26:35.47,opp,,0,0,0,,鯨魚們的每一聲悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.47,0:26:38.61,opp,,0,0,0,,失去的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.61,0:26:41.43,opp,,0,0,0,,珍愛的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.43,0:26:45.53,opp,,0,0,0,,我欲以這雙手緊緊抱住
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.72,0:26:49.16,opp,,0,0,0,,而如今依舊彷徨著去向
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.41,0:26:54.91,opp,,0,0,0,,琥珀色的太陽潛藏一切答案
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.31,0:26:58.15,opp,,0,0,0,,如果沒有遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.60,0:27:02.40,opp,,0,0,0,,我永遠只是一個只知殺戮的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.76,0:27:07.80,opp,,0,0,0,,擁有那永恆瞬間的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.64,0:27:11.92,opp,,0,0,0,,我的羽翼 想要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.41,0:27:19.04,opp,,0,0,0,,我就是為了瞭解這份愛而來到這世上
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.44,0:27:25.61,opp,,0,0,0,,從一萬二千年前便已愛上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.09,0:27:29.17,opp,,0,0,0,,歷經八千年的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.17,0:27:32.48,opp,,0,0,0,,只讓這份愛意更深
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.71,0:27:38.67,opp,,0,0,0,,任何語言也無法表達 我有多么的愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.26,0:27:40.26,opp,,0,0,0,,我愿獻出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.27,0:27:42.03,opp,,0,0,0,,獻出全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.40,0:27:45.57,opp,,0,0,0,,只為看到你每日的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.80,0:27:52.22,opp,,0,0,0,,即使再過一億年 我依然會深深愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.44,0:27:57.30,opp,,0,0,0,,從認識你的那一天開始 每一天 每一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.41,0:28:04.14,opp,,0,0,0,,我的地獄都充滿著音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.52,0:28:18.46,opp,,0,0,0,,一萬兩千年
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.32,0:28:23.06,opp,,0,0,0,,我一直愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.94,0:26:25.15,oppp,,0,0,0,,I remember sitting with you (sitting with you)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.17,0:26:28.94,oppp,,0,0,0,,Underneath the tree of life (Underneath the tree of life)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.97,0:26:31.87,oppp,,0,0,0,,We listened to every fainted cry
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.21,0:26:35.47,oppp,,0,0,0,,Of the creatures there on the day the world began
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.47,0:26:38.61,oppp,,0,0,0,,Looking at everything that I've lost (everything that I've lost)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.61,0:26:41.43,oppp,,0,0,0,,And almost everything that I've loved (everything that I've loved)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.43,0:26:45.53,oppp,,0,0,0,,I'll hold them all (in my arms) tightly in my arms
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.72,0:26:49.16,oppp,,0,0,0,,Wondering where I am, so please tell me where to go
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.41,0:26:54.91,oppp,,0,0,0,,All of the answers you seek lie hidden in the sun (a-qua-ri-on)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.31,0:26:58.15,oppp,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't met you my life
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.60,0:27:02.40,oppp,,0,0,0,,Would've been in the (Darkness forever)darkness forever
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.76,0:27:07.80,oppp,,0,0,0,,In my wings (In my wings) are the powers of immortality
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.64,0:27:11.92,oppp,,0,0,0,,But by meeting you (You) my whole life has changed (changed)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.41,0:27:19.04,oppp,,0,0,0,,You give light to me hope to me strength into my life
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.44,0:27:25.61,oppp,,0,0,0,,All this time these twelve thousand years I know Aishiteiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.09,0:27:29.17,oppp,,0,0,0,,Eight thousand years from the time that I've met you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.17,0:27:32.48,oppp,,0,0,0,,My love grows strong than ever before
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.71,0:27:38.67,oppp,,0,0,0,,Words can't say of this time I've been waiting to share my love with you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.26,0:27:40.26,oppp,,0,0,0,,I'd give you my life
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.27,0:27:42.03,oppp,,0,0,0,,I would give you the world
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.40,0:27:45.57,oppp,,0,0,0,,To see you smiling every day (smiling every day)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.80,0:27:52.22,oppp,,0,0,0,,One hundred million and two thousand years from now Aishiteiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.44,0:27:57.30,oppp,,0,0,0,,I want you to know since you came in my life every day every night
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.41,0:28:04.14,oppp,,0,0,0,,You give light into the darkest skies
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.52,0:28:18.46,oppp,,0,0,0,,All these twelve thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.32,0:28:23.06,oppp,,0,0,0,,I've been loving you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把御子乃還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無限拳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無限?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙也使出了無限拳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 總覺得哪裡不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拳頭居然先出現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因和結果的逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的拳頭超越了因果定律嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區翼犬也敢稱無限 真是可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:00:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神的力量才是無限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:01:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無處不在 又無時無刻不在賜予祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼到不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼到不了你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭讓阿馬塔這麼痛苦的合體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是未影的心靈迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我一死 未影就不能再操控太陽之翼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我人很笨 找不到其他阻止未影的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果失去了御子乃 阿馬塔就會傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想讓阿馬塔傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合體要解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為阿馬塔而死太不值得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渺小的無翅之眾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不再需要你們的身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的太陽之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其原本就該由太古諸神獨自披掛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦能將之喚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Element只要有被詛咒的新娘和我就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超念轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 就讓我敲響復仇的婚禮鐘聲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕望預知被改寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪取這可憎的女人的身體 我將孕育出新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從而成為創世之神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甦醒吧 另一個太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎 柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:06:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界各地的氣溫上升 海平面下降
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有河川、湖沼的水位正在不斷下降
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽之翼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使一切枯涸的灼熱之火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去世界會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是光靠Vector無法與他對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔 合體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是久違的合體呢 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix 你回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這曲子 難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認是修雷特此前所搭乘的機體無誤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…檢測不到有活體反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,檢測到新的Vector反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡所棄乘的Vector X 健在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一來預備的Vector就有兩台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要再有一台的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別忘了還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector Z 諸井在此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對生於南國的我來說 灼熱的太陽猶如朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就湊齊三台了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎 柚葉再度出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Element替換
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我頂替諸井
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克蕾亞理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太亂來了 那倒不如讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多納爾 須緒美 你們一定要活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如有萬一  你們就要成為下一個時代的亞當和夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎 柚葉 你們跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請走好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這曲子…修雷特?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點擔心你能否代替我作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是交給你了 摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是Jin所出生的星球還是地球我都想守護
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特 你用靈魂的旋律來協助我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了最親密的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了最心愛的伴侶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了最珍視的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:09:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了最寶貴的情意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們上吧 修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神友合體 Go Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感受到了 朋友的靈魂離我是這麼的近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 感受到了 你和大家的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且 聯繫在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心靈中的缺口也在被填滿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點一點地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步一步地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這便是不動所追求的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿越時空 共同書寫神話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion  GEPADA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 我們一起戰鬥吧 怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無謂的掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在 摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空間轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:11:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理事長…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開洞 開洞 開洞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攜手奉上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏聖葬送曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罔顧自己一把年紀過度操勞了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說一把年紀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡耍些小動作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空間填補
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放棄 絕不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使一再受傷 也能重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就這麼想要那個女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就在此做個了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩顆星球正在被強行拉到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在吸收星球的生命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是一萬二千年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 令人懷念的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波羅…是阿波羅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要悲傷 我最心愛的…未來的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誕生於天翅和無翅之間 讓我痛苦 而又拯救了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭翅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的錯 讓你們為了我的請求而犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論是你 還是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都只是做了那時自己力所能及的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且遵照約定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就這樣再次相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波羅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為人類和天翅得以結合了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一而再地奪走我所愛之人的可憎的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不動總司令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是為愛而生的頭翅所割捨掉的心靈陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心靈陰影…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要逃避 你還有必須正視的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克服恐懼 觸及真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的你一定辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波羅尼亞斯 阿波羅尼亞斯 阿波羅尼亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波羅尼亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要將你所珍愛的一切都燃燒殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合體被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只用一擊就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未影那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我力量吧 頹女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 你這個臭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詳情留待之後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 讓我們一起來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守護御子乃 還有這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋阿馬塔 這時候不應該說「抱歉」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 遲鈍的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然讓這種頹女人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忠愛合體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘊含在剛強裡的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱藏在怯弱裡的豪情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人愛不自已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波羅尼亞斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}阿波羅尼亞斯 阿波羅尼亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然如此深愛著阿波羅尼亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}阿波羅尼亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭受背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}阿波羅尼亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懷揣怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}阿波羅尼亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx85\fscy85}阿波羅尼亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也還如此地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波羅尼亞斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我愛你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 你是如此地…如此地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點 就還差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢正視奪你所愛的那份罪惡感 以及你的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今還有什麼好說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要如何處置我悉隨尊便
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…求你救救這個世界裡的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔 不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 大家快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我怎麼能拋棄御子乃你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這次不會再坐視不理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會連結起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛與悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被分割的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會連結給你們看的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一記 三位一體拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要被燒焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能夠放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那天眼睜睜看著媽媽離去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓自己一直後悔至今
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我終於明白到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一萬二千年前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾維亞…御子乃被我離棄時所感受到的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為了理解這份感受才會再次誕生到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這次我不會再坐視不理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要道別
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和心愛的人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和御子乃一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守護這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區一條翼犬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣…到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion 合體解除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Element 駕駛員心理等級過低
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話 阿瑪塔他們就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿瑪塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保護…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 Jin？ 是Jin嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過吧 柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人 絕不是孤獨的
