Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光憑一個人你還能如何連結 你還能連結什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為有某人在身邊 正因為思念著某人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能夠連結起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會永遠在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.56,0:23:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算御子乃年老色衰 長滿了皺紋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又或者這一刻永遠定格 化作神話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將永無止境地翱翔 永無止境地愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.26,0:23:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為了愛希爾菲才跨越一萬二千年的時光降生於此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.08,0:23:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.11,0:23:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻愛著現在 愛著現在的御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們攜手前往愛的彼岸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.46,0:23:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.31,0:23:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.48,0:23:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.46,0:23:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聖合體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.19,0:24:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GO Aquarion EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.62,0:24:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.98,0:24:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 不是EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.28,0:24:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的新名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.09,0:24:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.46,0:24:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.35,0:24:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.75,0:24:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.64,0:24:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.75,0:24:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛慕已久
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.37,0:24:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 在炫耀恩愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.47,0:25:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion LOVE的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.06,0:25:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿越了空間 滋潤乾涸的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.42,0:25:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將被割裂的世界逐漸連結到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.54,0:25:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…不能就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.69,0:25:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體 給我身體
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.42,0:25:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.17,0:25:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.84,0:25:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我不能隨心所欲地活動
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.08,0:25:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波羅尼亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.09,0:25:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來接納你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.93,0:25:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們一同看守著時代
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.64,0:26:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我體內沉睡吧 愛的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.88,0:26:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們超越了時空 在這個時代結合到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.10,0:26:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這明明是一再背叛我的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.66,0:26:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.14,0:26:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你體內會如此的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.06,0:27:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修修
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.54,0:28:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.79,0:28:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後 戀愛解禁
